1 Sac size change after fEVAR in GG&C

1.1 Scope of data

  • 86 primary fEVAR/bEVAR have been performed in Glasgow
  • The first fEVAR was performed in 17 December 2009 using Cook Zenith stent-graft
  • Glasgow then switched to Terumo Aortic (then Vascutek) Anaconda device and performed 28 fEVAR between 23 May 2011 and 13 July 2020
  • Glasgow returned to the Zenith platform in 03 February 2020 and has performed a total of 58 fEVAR up until 16 June 2023

1.2 Sac size change

  • The following plot shows sac size change after fEVAR (or bEVAR) for all cases
  • Both juxta-renal and thoraco-abdominal cases are included
